 got a special Miss Santa@costume and everything."},{"chara":[{"cheek":0,"face":"mtn_ex_030.exp.json","id":101850}],"textLeft":"Yes..."},{"chara":[{"id":802000,"lipSynch":0}],"textRight":"..."},{"chara":[{"id":101850,"lipSynch":0}],"textLeft":"..."},{"chara":[{"cheek":0,"face":"mtn_ex_010.exp.json","id":802000}],"textRight":"Um, about what you mentioned before."},{"chara":[{"cheek":0,"face":"mtn_ex_050.exp.json","id":101850,"motion":0}],"textLeft":"Yes?"},{"chara":[{"id":802000}],"textRight":"You said you looked up to Miss Santa since you@were little."},{"chara":[{"id":802000}],"textRight":"Was there some special reason?"},{"bgm":"stop","chara":[{"id":101850}],"textLeft":"Oh...why yes, there was!"},{"bgm":"bgm03_story03","chara":[{"cheek":0,"face":"mtn_ex_011.exp.json","id":101850,"motion":1}],"textLeft":"This happened years ago... I was still@just a child."},{"chara":[{"id":101850}],"textLeft":"It was around this time of year... Christmas@was growing closer and closer."},{"autoTurnLast":0.01,"chara":[{"cheek":1,"face":"mtn_ex_030.exp.json","id":801600,"motion":0,"pos":1}],"turnChangeIn":"fadeIn"},{"bg":"bg_adv_15024.jpg","nameNarration":"Tsukuyo","narration":"\"I was with my mother, shopping for gifts in@town when suddenly, I realized I got lost.\"","narrationBg":"","narrationCoverOpacity":110.0,"narrationEffect":"in","turnChangeOut":"fadeOut","turnEffect":"sepiaFrame"},{"narration":"\"And to make matters worse,@I tripped and fell... My dear flute@that I was holding got scratched.\""},{"narration":"\"I was sobbing inconsolably, and that@was when Miss Santa appeared!\""},{"autoTurnLast":0.01,"item":[{"path":"resource/scenario/img/50450_tower_christmas18/memoria_1289.jpg","posX":0,"posY":0,"visible":"appear"}],"narrationEffect":"out","turnChangeIn":"fadeIn"},{"nameNarration":"Tsukuyo","narration":"— Tsukuyo —@Miss Santa took me to the area where@lost children can be picked up.","narrationAnchor":"bottom","narrationCoverOpacity":110.0,"narrationEffect":"in","narrationFontSize":28.0,"narrationLineMargin":15.0,"narrationLineSpace":10.0,"turnChangeOut":"fadeOut"},{"narration":"— Tsukuyo —@\"Let me borrow this for a moment,\"@she said, and took my flute."},{"narration":"— Tsukuyo —@When she gave it back to me,@it was fixed and gleaming brightly."},{"narration":"— Tsukuyo —@When I asked, \"How did you fix it?\"@she told me this:"},{"narration":"— Tsukuyo —@\"Hee hee... Well, I'm Miss Santa.\""},{"narration":"— Tsukuyo —@\"I can use magic that makes everyone@feel happy.\" That is what she told me!"},{"autoTurnLast":0.01,"bg":"bg_adv_21334.jpg","chara":[{"cheek":0,"face":"mtn_ex_011.exp.json","id":101850,"motion":1,"pos":0},{"cheek":0,"face":"mtn_ex_050.exp.json","id":802000,"motion":0,"pos":2}],"item":[{"path":"resource/scenario/img/50450_tower_christmas18/memoria_1289.jpg","visible":"hide"}],"narrationEffect":"out","turnChangeIn":"fadeIn","turnEffect":"stop"},{"chara":[{"id":101850}],"textLeft":"After that, I was reunited with my mother at@the pickup spot.","turnChangeOut":"fadeOut"},{"chara":[{"id":101850}],"textLeft":"Ever since that happened, I have been@enamored with Miss Santa!"},{"chara":[{"id":802000}],"textRight":"I see..."},{"chara":[{"cheek":0,"face":"mtn_ex_011.exp.json","id":802000}],"textRight":"So that's why you dressed up as Miss Santa."},{"chara":[{"id":101850,"motion":100}],"textLeft":"Precisely!"},{"autoTurnLast":0.01,"item":[{"path":"resource/scenario/img/50450_tower_christmas18/memoria_1289.jpg","posX":0,"posY":0,"visible":"appear"}],"turnChangeIn":"fadeIn"},{"nameNarration":"Tsukuyo","narration":"— Tsukuyo —@Wearing this costume...fills me@with memories of that time.","narrationAnchor":"bottom","narrationCoverOpacity":110.0,"narrationEffect":"in","narrationFontSize":28.0,"narrationLineMargin":15.0,"narrationLineSpace":10.0,"turnChangeOut":"fadeOut","turnEffect":"sepiaFrame"},{"narration":"— Tsukuyo —@I had it custom-ordered to look@as much like hers as possible."},{"autoTurnLast":0.01,"chara":[{"cheek":0,"face":"mtn_ex_011.exp.json","id":101850,"motion":0,"pos":0},{"cheek":0,"face":"mtn_ex_050.exp.json","id":802000,"motion":0,"pos":2}],"item":[{"path":"resource/scenario/img/50450_tower_christmas18/memoria_1289.jpg","visible":"hide"}],"narrationEffect":"out","turnChangeIn":"fadeIn","turnEffect":"stop"},{"chara":[{"id":802000,"lipSynch":0}],"textRight":"...","turnChangeOut":"fadeOut"},{"chara":[{"cheek":0,"face":"mtn_ex_050.exp.json","id":101850}],"textLeft":"Oh, sorry."},{"chara":[{"cheek":0,"face":"mtn_ex_030.exp.json","id":101850,"motion":300}],"textLeft":"Her fixing my flute with magic, and so on."},{"chara":[{"id":101850}],"textLeft":"I know it sounds like a fairy tale that@no one would ever believe..."},{"chara":[{"cheek":0,"face":"mtn_ex_010.exp.json","id":802000}],"textRight":"No."},{"chara":[{"id":802000}],"textRight":"Christmas magic is definitely a real thing."},{"chara":[{"cheek":0,"face":"mtn_ex_040.exp.json","id":101850,"motion":100}],"textLeft":"You believe me?"},{"chara":[{"id":802000}],"textRight":"Of course!"},{"chara":[{"cheek":0,"face":"mtn_ex_050.exp.json","id":802000}],"textRight":"Come to think of it..."},{"chara":[{"cheek":0,"face":"mtn_ex_010.exp.json","id":802000}],"textRight":"Why don't you try calling that girl you@wanted to meet up with one last time?"},{"chara":[{"cheek":0,"face":"mtn_ex_011.exp.json","id":101850,"motion":200}],"textLeft":"Good idea!"},{"autoTurnLast":2.0,"turnChangeIn":"fadeIn"}]},"version":3}